{"tid":2507480,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[回憶] 一人一篇印象深刻嘅中文課文","createTime":"2021-04-28T04:39:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T04:39:19.000Z","uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c7bced8d964a34d4385db2dc108d1d275fc50855","tid":2507480,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"又到DSE季節，係時候重溫中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n白話文嘅話我最記得有篇叫「爸爸的花兒落了」，可能因為個名夠搞笑，所以特別記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣啲同學仲係咁叫佢做媽媽的Bra兒落了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過內容係咩已經唔係好記得，淨係記得嗰棵花係夾竹桃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋又有咩深刻嘅文？<br />\n白話/文言文都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}